---
import Next from '../components/Next.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="py-8 px-4">
    <h1 class="mb-8">May</h1>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 pb-4">
      <img src="/may/gaw.JPG" />
      <img src="/may/serve.JPG" />
    </div>
    <p>I watched you play volleyball 🏐 in May!! I was so happy watching you play!</p>

    <div class="relative pt-8 pb-4 h-[420px]">
      <img src="/may/nagi.JPG" class="w-1/2 absolute rounded left-4 rotate-3" />
      <img src="/may/yum.JPG" class="w-1/2 absolute rounded -rotate-2 right-4 translate-y-32" />
    </div>
    <p>Food is a staple in our relationship 😋 I remember you LOVED the Meet Fresh!!</p>
    <div class="relative pt-8 pb-4">
      <img src="/may/matcha.JPG" class="rounded" />
    </div>
    <p>REMEMBER THIS?!?! We're really meant for each other</p>
    <div class="relative pt-8 pb-4">
      <img src="/may/mom.JPG" class="rounded" />
    </div>
    <p>We also celebrated your mom's birthday!</p>
    <Next to="/june" title="June will forever be in my heart" />
  </section>
</Layout>
